`8Keywords``   : Warfare
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

The warfare skillgroup is aimed at giving the warrior an edge in combat by
weakening the victim sufficiently to allow the warrior to beat the victim  at
melee combat. All warfare skills can only be used to initiate combat. ``  

 * sweep	     an area attack for warriors
 * stun 	     a skill aimed at slowing the victim down
 * fury 	     allows the warrior to enter combat in a rage
 * diminish	     lowers the victim's strength
 * crush	     a skill aimed at lowering the victim's defenses
 ``

